USAGE:
------------

NOTE: The index.html file is pointing to an arbitrary UUID resource.
      This UUID represents the unique client connection.

1) Run examples/ex.php
2) Visit:  examples/index.html in your browser
     This subsequently attaches to the 'ex.php' server on port 20000 via the 'EventSource' object
3) To send a message from server to this client, run the following from command line:
     curl -XPOST localhost:9499/04ea2a5700e84891c547183db020608e -d '"Hello World"'
